graphs.text: #   This page spans the two outermost verso panels (f102v3, f102v2) of
#   a six-panel fold-out. Panel f102v3 is half-width.
#   Two blocks of text and three rows of plants:
#      [2,1]..[2,7] just below first row: more leaves.
#      [3,1]..[3,5] between the two text blocks: roots with leaves.
#    Plant 4 of the last row has "same" label as
#    first plant on top row of f89v1.  The root is similar,
# The first three labels may be attached to the leaf at left
# leaf [1,3] - long wing-shaped leaf, triangular root?
# item [1,4] - "cube root" - one dark side, three light sides
# leaf [1,5] - short wing-shaped leaf - dark,light edges
# leaf [2,2] comb-shaped leaf with knob-shaped fingers
# leaf [2,3] - comb-shaped leaf with knob-shaped fingers and sharp "claws"
# leaf [2,4] - pine-like leaves, thin light stem
# leaf [2,5] - leaf with six clubsuit-shaped fingers
# leaf [2,6] - round leaf with many knob-shaped fingers
# leaf [2,7] - cypress-like plant with chestnut-like tuber
# plant [3,1] - small root, light stems, big horned  serrated leaves
# plant [3,3] - "carrot" plant - dark leaves, light stems, carrot
# plant [3,4] - round serrated leaf, bundle of long mousetail roots
# plant [3,5] - round serrated leaf, bundle of long mousetail roots,
# label faded at edge of page
